"""Test get_rdfs_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_rdfs_stats(rdfs_group_id=self.p_data.rdfs_group_id,
    metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now, end_time=self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.RDFS))
